txt.en: 'I thank you for rescuing Gondorians in Dor-en-Ernil. Though these are dark times, they shall live another day, and it gives me hope.'

Erchar's warriors hope to rescue any refugees fleeing from the enemy in Dor-en-Ernil.

'Dor-en-Ernil is a rural land, but its coast thrives with fishermen and merchants. We warriors are few in this region and I fear many folk fleeing for their lives may need assistance.

'Save those that you come across on your journeys through Dor-en-Ernil and we shall do the same.'

<rgb=#FF0000>This bounty can only be completed a maximum of three times.</rgb>
Gondorian refugees can be found just south of Tungobel in central Dor-en-Ernil.\n\nSeek out and rescue any refugees in Dor-en-Ernil.
